<taxonomicName authority="Fraser, 1912" authorityName="Fraser" authorityYear="1912" box="[227,478,712,738]" class="Hydrozoa" family="Hebellidae" genus="Scandia" kingdom="Animalia" order="Leptothecata" pageId="26" pageNumber="27" phylum="Cnidaria" rank="genus">
<emphasis box="[227,321,712,737]" italics="true" pageId="26" pageNumber="27">Scandia</emphasis>
<bibRefCitation author="Fraser" box="[328,478,712,738]" pageId="26" pageNumber="50" refString="Fraser, C. M. (1912) Some hydroids of Beaufort, North Carolina. Bulletin of the United States Bureau of Fisheries, 30, 339 - 387." type="journal article" year="1912">
Fraser, 
<number box="[415,478,712,738]" pageId="26" pageNumber="27" value="1912.0">1912</number>
</bibRefCitation>
</taxonomicName>
. No positive identification is possible in the absence of gonothecae.
</paragraph>
</subSubSection>
